metadata.name: Death
metadata.description:
Death which is a colorful tree hugs you like a kind mother.
Life steals its color from death but actually it's gray and neutral.
It tries to attract people to itself with the color of death but if you look carefully you can see the blood of life and that is gray and its real hand which is gray too.
Death tries hard to clean this mess of life's shitshow, that's why she has become black
